          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Finally, one of the stilt-horses kneels down low enough that you are\nable to climb onto its back. You balance there cautiously, your sore\nbum reminding you of the last two times you tried this. But this time,\nthe stilt-horse seems perfectly content with you as its rider."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You remember what the locals told you. The horses will let you ride\nthem, but only for the day. This herd always returns to Meadow when\nnight falls."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Choose one Ranger to ride the stilt-horse. That Ranger attaches it to\ntheir role. Remove all"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress",
              "color": "black"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "from this card. Write down"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "ACCEPTED AS A RIDER"
            }
          ],
          "color": "blue"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
